Package autoscope.utils

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AutoscopeTestInterface
    Implemented by every module's ****TestBase.java to ensure all necessary parameters are provided for configuring applications
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidUtils
    Contains methods exclusive to Android devices
    AutoscopeUtils
    Contains methods that can be used for network and interruption tests on both Android/iOS (phone call, power cycle, SMS, etc.) Contains methods for debugging purposes
    ContactBuilder
    Called to generate information for a random contact
    IOSUtils
    Contains methods exclusive to iOS devices
    RetryAnalyzer
    Listener that sets the number of retries for a test session depending on the test result
    RetryListener
    Sets the RetryAnalyzer.java class as the listener for retries
    TestListener
    Listener that controls all parts of the test run
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AndroidVirtualDevices
    Contains all the Android virtual devices in use
    IOSSimulators
    Contains all the iOS Simulators in use
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AutoscopeRunOptions
    Used to switch between Autoscope driver, virtual devices, simulators, and test environment.
